This project was developed as part of a Master's thesis at Stockholm University:
"Designing Privacy-Preserving Home Security Camera System for Shared Living Spaces: A Human-Centered Study of Real-Time Face Blurring and Everyday Privacy."

This repository contains original source code and documentation for the Edge Privacy Camera research prototype.

